data.description: Beautifully renovated and move-in ready 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom split level home in the Christian Hills Community in the Salem High School District. The main level features a beautiful fireside great room, open concept dining room, kitchen with stainless steel appliances, owners suite with ensuite bath, 2 secondary bedrooms and a full bathroom. The lower level features a fireside flex room with a wet bar, full bedroom, full bathroom, laundry room and 2 car garage with side entry. The backyard has a beautiful deck overlooking the fenced in backyard and also features 2 outbuildings. This beautiful cul-de-sac home is waiting for YOU! Come check it out today!
